<plot>'The End of War' follows the story of Thomas, an American soldier who enlists in the military and goes to the front lines. The setting and era shifts as he experiences war, moving from 1777 to 2006. The Revolution, Civil War, WWI, WWII, Vietnam, and Iraq are all covered and the different faces of battle are examined in our nation's history and the common themes throughout.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?555361</url></doc>
